Trains Meadow Road (non-existent since prior to 1909, when it was a private lane in the Konwenhoven Estate property) west side north of Astoria Avenue. This house is either in the line of 85th Street; or on either side of it between Twenty-third and Twenty-fourth Avenues. It may also be on the north side of Astoria Avenue between 84th and 85th Streets.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
